AVbin 10 for pyglet
===================

Redistributable package for AVbin to use with pyglet (www.pyglet.org). Please respect the license in COPYING.LESSER.

Usage
-----
In your installer or package include the avbin library for the specific platform and install it in the same location
of your application executable or a `lib` directory directly underneath. Make sure your application enables loading
libraries from the local directory::

  pyglet.options['search_local_libs'] = True
